    "query": "What are the operational requirements for a registered credit rating agency regarding its client monitoring and rating processes?",
    "golden_answer": "A registered credit rating agency is required to monitor all significant changes concerning its client companies and must establish efficient, responsive systems to ensure that the ratings it provides are both timely and accurate.",
