  {
    "query": "What are the requirements for parties involved in an Investment Trust regarding their roles and responsibilities under the IFSCA (Fund Management) Regulations, 2025?",
    "golden_answer": "Under the IFSCA (Fund Management) Regulations, 2025, parties to an Investment Trust are required to perform their roles and discharge their responsibilities in accordance with the specifications set out in the Fourth Schedule.",
