  {
    "query": "What are the specific criteria used to determine if a person meets the 'fit and proper' requirement under the IFSCA (TechFin and Ancillary Services) Regulations, 2025?",
    "golden_answer": "To be considered 'fit and proper', a person must demonstrate a record of fairness and integrity, which specifically includes financial integrity, a good reputation and character, and honesty.",
