  {
    "query": "What is the minimum experience requirement for Key Managerial Personnel (KMP) as specified under sub-regulation (2) of the IFSCA (Fund Management) Regulations, 2025?",
    "golden_answer": "For the Key Managerial Personnel (KMP) referred to under sub-regulation (2), the required experience in related activities in the securities market or financial products in an eligible institution is a minimum period of 3 years.",
