  {
    "query": "Which individuals and entities within a Fund Management Entity (FME) are required to adhere to the Code of Conduct outlined in the Third Schedule of the IFSCA (Fund Management) Regulations, 2025?",
    "golden_answer": "Every FME, fiduciaries, and Key Managerial Personnel (KMPs)—which specifically includes the Principal Officer, Fund Managers, and the Designated Compliance Officer—are required to abide by the Code of Conduct specified in the Third Schedule.",
