    "query": "What criteria must a Venture Capital scheme follow when making investments under sub-regulation (1)?",
    "golden_answer": "Investments made under sub-regulation (1) must comply with the provisions of the IFSCA (Fund Management) Regulations, 2025, align with the investment objective of the Venture Capital scheme, and adhere to the disclosures provided in the placement memorandum.",
